WEBVTT

00:00:05.806 --> 00:00:08.141 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

00:00:50.058 --> 00:00:53.770 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:01:04.656 --> 00:01:05.782 line:80%
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

00:01:05.866 --> 00:01:07.784 line:80%
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

00:01:07.868 --> 00:01:10.495 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:01:34.936 --> 00:01:35.770 line:80%
[grunts]

00:01:41.526 --> 00:01:44.112 line:80%
[grunts, whimpers]

00:01:45.780 --> 00:01:47.073 line:80%
[grunts]

00:01:54.664 --> 00:01:55.916 line:80%
[grunts]

00:02:00.587 --> 00:02:02.172 line:80%
[tires screeching]

00:02:08.136 --> 00:02:09.220 line:80%
[♪ tense music continues]

00:02:10.305 --> 00:02:11.306 line:80%
[grunts]

00:02:19.272 --> 00:02:20.273 line:80%
[grunts]

00:02:38.833 --> 00:02:41.169 line:80%
[Huiju breathing heavily]

00:02:48.677 --> 00:02:51.096 line:80%
[muffled footsteps]

00:02:54.557 --> 00:02:55.642 line:80%
[sighs]

00:02:58.561 --> 00:03:00.730 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:03:11.408 --> 00:03:13.660 line:80%
[breathing heavily]

00:03:17.372 --> 00:03:22.085 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

00:03:23.044 --> 00:03:24.045 line:20%
[Yun] An accident?

00:03:24.546 --> 00:03:25.714 line:20%
What have you heard exactly?

00:03:25.797 --> 00:03:28.091 line:20%
Only that there was a collision.

00:03:28.174 --> 00:03:30.635 line:20%
[♪ sorrowful music playing]

00:03:32.262 --> 00:03:33.638 line:20%
I need to be there.

00:03:35.473 --> 00:03:36.808 line:20%
Do not just stand there.

00:03:36.891 --> 00:03:38.435 line:20%
Prepare to leave at once!

00:03:38.518 --> 00:03:39.769 line:20%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:03:42.689 --> 00:03:48.194 line:20%
THE ROYAL SEOUL HOSPITAL

00:03:51.448 --> 00:03:53.199 line:80%
How did this happen?

00:03:53.783 --> 00:03:54.784 line:80%
What about His Majesty?

00:03:54.868 --> 00:03:57.037 line:80%
Was there an attack on His Majesty's life?

00:03:58.371 --> 00:03:59.914 line:80%
Say something!

00:03:59.998 --> 00:04:01.374 line:80%
Please calm down, Your Majesty.

00:04:05.045 --> 00:04:08.048 line:80%
His scans reveal no fractures
or internal injuries.

00:04:08.131 --> 00:04:09.924 line:80%
Just some minor bruising.

00:04:10.008 --> 00:04:11.259 line:80%
[sighs]

00:04:33.990 --> 00:04:35.075 line:80%
And the Grand Prince?

00:04:35.658 --> 00:04:37.535 line:80%
I heard he was at the scene as well.

00:04:38.286 --> 00:04:39.704 line:80%
Is he all right?

00:04:42.749 --> 00:04:44.042 line:80%
He is in surgery.

00:04:44.751 --> 00:04:47.253 line:80%
It appears his left shoulder bore
much of the impact.

00:04:48.088 --> 00:04:50.757 line:80%
It seems he has done everything
in his power to stop the car.

00:04:51.883 --> 00:04:52.884 line:80%
[secretary] Prime Minister Min.

00:04:55.011 --> 00:04:56.012 line:80%
May I have a word?

00:04:58.389 --> 00:04:59.599 line:80%
[sighs]

00:05:07.315 --> 00:05:08.316 line:80%
[sighs]

00:05:11.486 --> 00:05:13.988 line:80%
Photos of the accident
have spread on social media.

00:05:14.072 --> 00:05:15.698 line:80%
Her conspicuous vehicle didn't help.

00:05:15.782 --> 00:05:17.867 line:80%
How is Ms. Seong doing?

00:05:17.951 --> 00:05:20.870 line:80%
She's still unconscious,
but the scans have come back clean.

00:05:21.704 --> 00:05:24.874 line:80%
Hmm. Are photos of the escort vehicles
also circulating?

00:05:24.958 --> 00:05:28.294 line:80%
No. They were some distance away
from the scene,

00:05:28.378 --> 00:05:30.130 line:80%
and we're removing them as they appear.

00:05:30.213 --> 00:05:31.214 line:80%
That should be enough.

00:05:31.297 --> 00:05:32.715 line:80%
Pushing too hard will raise--

00:05:32.799 --> 00:05:34.092 line:80%
What did you just say?

00:05:37.971 --> 00:05:40.932 line:80%
What does Ms. Seong Huiju
have to do with any of this?

00:05:47.105 --> 00:05:49.107 line:80%
Are you saying the vehicle involved,

00:05:49.858 --> 00:05:52.652 line:80%
the one His Majesty was in,
belongs to that woman?

00:05:54.279 --> 00:05:57.240 line:80%
[♪ ominous music playing]

00:05:59.534 --> 00:06:00.535 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:06:04.998 --> 00:06:06.040 line:80%
Where are you going?

00:06:09.294 --> 00:06:11.462 line:80%
Must I report such things to you?

00:06:16.968 --> 00:06:17.969 line:80%
The wise decision

00:06:18.970 --> 00:06:21.431 line:80%
would be to not go anywhere.

00:06:24.267 --> 00:06:26.895 line:80%
The people know
Ms. Seong's vehicle was involved.

00:06:27.854 --> 00:06:28.855 line:80%
So?

00:06:28.938 --> 00:06:30.690 line:80%
"His Majesty was in that car

00:06:30.773 --> 00:06:33.026 line:80%
and the Grand Prince caused
an accident to save him,

00:06:33.109 --> 00:06:36.529 line:80%
racking up countless traffic violations
and substantial damage in the process."

00:06:37.155 --> 00:06:38.740 line:80%
If word of this got out,

00:06:38.823 --> 00:06:39.824 line:80%
all of this could be blamed

00:06:40.950 --> 00:06:42.035 line:80%
on the young king.

00:06:43.870 --> 00:06:44.871 line:80%
Prime Minister Min.

00:06:44.954 --> 00:06:47.207 line:80%
I am merely stating that it could lead

00:06:47.957 --> 00:06:49.083 line:80%
to such dire conclusions.

00:06:51.669 --> 00:06:53.338 line:80%
Are you trying to protect that maiden?

00:06:54.964 --> 00:06:57.133 line:80%
I am trying to protect the Crown.

00:07:05.308 --> 00:07:07.185 line:80%
OPERATING CENTER

00:07:08.603 --> 00:07:09.854 line:20%
PATIENT: LEE ***
IN RECOVERY

00:07:12.357 --> 00:07:13.566 line:80%
[music ends]

00:07:16.527 --> 00:07:17.862 line:80%
[surgeon] The surgery went well.

00:07:18.363 --> 00:07:19.989 line:80%
The anesthesia has just worn off,

00:07:20.073 --> 00:07:23.159 line:80%
so he should be able to go up
to his room in about an hour.

00:07:24.994 --> 00:07:27.121 line:80%
What about any lasting effects?

00:07:27.205 --> 00:07:31.292 line:80%
I heard it can be difficult
to use your arm after shoulder surgery.

00:07:31.376 --> 00:07:33.962 line:80%
The surgery wasn't due to a fracture
or a chronic condition,

00:07:34.045 --> 00:07:35.171 line:80%
so that is unlikely.

00:07:35.838 --> 00:07:37.173 line:80%
-No need to worry.
-Thank you.

00:07:37.257 --> 00:07:39.092 line:80%
-Thank you, Doctor.
-Thank you.

00:07:40.510 --> 00:07:41.719 line:80%
Thank goodness.

00:07:41.803 --> 00:07:43.096 line:80%
-That's a relief.
-Yes.

00:07:44.222 --> 00:07:46.516 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:07:54.983 --> 00:07:56.401 line:80%
[sighs]

00:08:08.371 --> 00:08:10.957 line:80%
Let's increase security
on the floor Ms. Seong is on.

00:08:11.040 --> 00:08:12.792 line:80%
-Send people from our office.
-Yes, sir.

00:08:12.875 --> 00:08:14.752 line:80%
Let me know as soon as she wakes up.

00:08:14.836 --> 00:08:16.045 line:80%
[secretary] Yes, sir.

00:08:29.309 --> 00:08:30.852 line:20%
VIP ROOM 5: SEONG HUIJU

00:08:53.082 --> 00:08:54.917 line:80%
[King crying]

00:08:56.836 --> 00:08:58.296 line:80%
[engine revs]

00:08:59.172 --> 00:09:00.840 line:80%
-[crashing]
-[tires screeching]

00:09:08.806 --> 00:09:10.892 line:80%
Ms. Seong.

00:09:13.519 --> 00:09:14.604 line:80%
Your Majesty?

00:09:15.271 --> 00:09:17.065 line:80%
Are you awake?

00:09:20.276 --> 00:09:22.278 line:80%
Your Majesty! Are you all right?

00:09:23.321 --> 00:09:24.572 line:80%
Is anything broken?

00:09:24.655 --> 00:09:26.240 line:80%
[breathes shakily]

00:09:26.324 --> 00:09:27.450 line:80%
[King] I am sorry.

00:09:29.118 --> 00:09:31.996 line:80%
This all happened
because I insisted on a drive.

00:09:35.541 --> 00:09:36.542 line:80%
Not at all.

00:09:37.752 --> 00:09:39.796 line:80%
Your Majesty and I are both fine.

00:09:43.883 --> 00:09:45.259 line:80%
Wait, His Royal Highness.

00:09:45.968 --> 00:09:47.970 line:80%
Where is the Grand Prince?
Is he here as well?

00:09:48.054 --> 00:09:49.639 line:80%
Do not worry.

00:09:49.722 --> 00:09:52.266 line:80%
Uncle did not faint.

00:09:52.350 --> 00:09:54.811 line:80%
He even went into the operating room
without crying.

00:09:55.311 --> 00:09:57.355 line:80%
The operating room?

00:09:57.438 --> 00:09:59.816 line:80%
He's having surgery?

00:10:00.566 --> 00:10:03.069 line:80%
Would you like some water?

00:10:03.820 --> 00:10:05.321 line:80%
[Huiju] Is the surgery over?

00:10:05.405 --> 00:10:06.406 line:80%
Are you okay?

00:10:07.657 --> 00:10:08.658 line:80%
[sighs]

00:10:08.741 --> 00:10:10.910 line:80%
I mean, what were you thinking,
jumping in there?

00:10:10.993 --> 00:10:12.078 line:80%
Are you insane?

00:10:12.578 --> 00:10:15.706 line:80%
Ms. Seong, His Royal Highness
has just woken up from the anesthesia…

00:10:15.790 --> 00:10:17.417 line:80%
-You can't just--
-Hold on.

00:10:18.209 --> 00:10:20.378 line:80%
You even hurt your face?

00:10:20.461 --> 00:10:22.630 line:80%
When that's all you have going for you?

00:10:23.423 --> 00:10:24.507 line:80%
[Huiju sighs]

00:10:29.679 --> 00:10:30.680 line:80%
Oh, no.

00:10:32.056 --> 00:10:33.057 line:80%
How are you doing?

00:10:35.351 --> 00:10:37.228 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:10:37.311 --> 00:10:38.312 line:80%
You were unconscious.

00:10:41.399 --> 00:10:42.442 line:80%
I'm perfectly fine.

00:10:54.620 --> 00:10:55.621 line:80%
Come here.

00:11:00.835 --> 00:11:01.961 line:80%
I'm hurting.

00:11:31.115 --> 00:11:32.241 line:80%
Anywhere else?

00:11:34.744 --> 00:11:35.745 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:11:39.499 --> 00:11:41.000 line:80%
[sighs]

00:11:47.590 --> 00:11:48.591 line:80%
[clears throat]

00:11:51.677 --> 00:11:53.596 line:80%
Don't ever jump in like that again.

00:11:56.891 --> 00:11:59.477 line:80%
I need to you stay in one piece
so you can have my back.

00:12:00.686 --> 00:12:02.563 line:80%
You were lucky this time.

00:12:02.647 --> 00:12:05.191 line:80%
Imagine if your life
was in danger… [shivers]

00:12:05.274 --> 00:12:07.735 line:80%
You think it would end
with just a few eggs?

00:12:08.277 --> 00:12:10.238 line:80%
Then stop putting me in that position.

00:12:13.324 --> 00:12:14.617 line:80%
I can't promise you that.

00:12:15.993 --> 00:12:17.161 line:80%
Then I can't either.

00:12:19.914 --> 00:12:22.833 line:80%
You make it seem like
you're madly in love with me.

00:12:25.878 --> 00:12:27.755 line:80%
This is what should be
making the headlines.

00:12:29.257 --> 00:12:30.466 line:80%
[sighs]

00:12:31.300 --> 00:12:32.301 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:12:36.055 --> 00:12:37.056 line:80%
[sighs]

00:12:38.015 --> 00:12:39.934 line:80%
[vehicles passing]

00:12:40.851 --> 00:12:42.436 line:80%
Babe, you sure this is right?

00:12:42.520 --> 00:12:44.146 line:80%
Yeah, you're almost there.

00:12:44.230 --> 00:12:45.314 line:80%
Okay.

00:12:45.398 --> 00:12:48.401 line:80%
Now put one hand on your chest. <i>Namaste.</i>

00:12:48.484 --> 00:12:49.777 line:80%
What? <i>Nama</i>-what-now?

00:12:49.860 --> 00:12:51.279 line:80%
<i>Namaste.</i>

00:12:51.362 --> 00:12:53.573 line:80%
Right. <i>Nama</i>…

00:12:53.656 --> 00:12:55.241 line:20%
FATHER (PICK UP WITHIN 3 SEC)

00:12:56.075 --> 00:12:57.702 line:80%
-Babe, Father's calling.
-What?

00:12:57.785 --> 00:12:59.328 line:80%
Now? Why?

00:12:59.412 --> 00:13:01.289 line:80%
-Does he know you're not at work?
-Darn it.

00:13:04.208 --> 00:13:05.334 line:80%
It's not even 8:00 yet.

00:13:05.835 --> 00:13:07.587 line:80%
That's true. Did you do something wrong?

00:13:07.670 --> 00:13:08.671 line:80%
No, I didn't.

00:13:09.213 --> 00:13:10.214 line:80%
Hello, Father.

00:13:11.132 --> 00:13:13.259 line:80%
What? Seong Huiju did?

00:13:13.926 --> 00:13:16.012 line:80%
What in the… Babe, turn the TV on.

00:13:18.180 --> 00:13:19.181 line:80%
Yes.

00:13:19.974 --> 00:13:23.978 line:80%
<i>Last night, a traffic accident occurred</i>
<i>on an outlying road in Gyeonggi Province.</i>

00:13:24.061 --> 00:13:25.980 line:80%
<i>-A speeding sports car</i>
-Yes, just a moment.

00:13:26.063 --> 00:13:28.399 line:80%
<i>collided with a vehicle</i>
<i>in the adjacent lane.</i>

00:13:28.482 --> 00:13:31.152 line:20%
<i>The driver of the sports car</i>
<i>was identified as CEO Seong Huiju</i>

00:13:31.235 --> 00:13:33.696 line:20%
<i>of Castle Beauty,</i>
<i>sparking further controversy.</i>

00:13:33.779 --> 00:13:35.906 line:80%
<i>It is being reported</i>
<i>that Ms. Seong's vehicle</i>

00:13:35.990 --> 00:13:37.867 line:80%
<i>was traveling 50 km/h</i>
<i>over the speed limit…</i>

00:13:37.950 --> 00:13:40.202 line:80%
-What do we do?
-Father, we'll come to you now.

00:13:40.286 --> 00:13:43.039 line:80%
<i>-The police are still investigating…</i>
-All right.

00:13:43.706 --> 00:13:44.749 line:80%
You can't come in here.

00:13:45.458 --> 00:13:47.793 line:80%
Seriously? Don't you remember me
from last time?

00:13:47.877 --> 00:13:49.545 line:80%
I'm her assistant at Castle Beauty.

00:13:49.629 --> 00:13:51.172 line:80%
You can't. Please step back.

00:13:51.255 --> 00:13:53.049 line:80%
[sighs] This is driving me insane.

00:13:54.091 --> 00:13:55.134 line:80%
Then what about him?

00:13:57.845 --> 00:14:00.848 line:80%
Come on! Why do you only ever stop me?

00:14:01.682 --> 00:14:02.892 line:80%
Ms. Seong!

00:14:02.975 --> 00:14:04.685 line:80%
Ms. Do, come here.

00:14:06.312 --> 00:14:07.480 line:80%
She's with me.

00:14:08.689 --> 00:14:10.483 line:80%
Those jerks are the worst.

00:14:11.942 --> 00:14:12.943 line:80%
Unbelievable.

00:14:14.153 --> 00:14:15.196 line:80%
Why do they keep…

00:14:16.155 --> 00:14:17.573 line:80%
[Huiju laughs]

00:14:17.657 --> 00:14:20.159 line:80%
I told you I'm fine.

00:14:20.701 --> 00:14:21.994 line:80%
Nothing to worry about.

00:14:22.078 --> 00:14:24.038 line:80%
I'm totally fine.

00:14:24.789 --> 00:14:25.998 line:80%
You'll fix this, right?

00:14:30.044 --> 00:14:31.504 line:80%
LIVE 3-MIN CHART

00:14:31.587 --> 00:14:33.673 line:80%
This was all part of the plan, right?

00:14:33.756 --> 00:14:37.051 line:80%
The chairman is freaking out.
He wants you as soon as you're discharged.

00:14:39.220 --> 00:14:40.304 line:80%
He knows I was injured?

00:14:40.388 --> 00:14:41.639 line:80%
Of course…

00:14:45.559 --> 00:14:47.019 line:80%
he does.

00:14:47.103 --> 00:14:48.896 line:80%
And still, not a single word?

00:14:49.730 --> 00:14:51.607 line:80%
Not from Father, or even Seong Taeju?

00:14:54.110 --> 00:14:56.529 line:80%
I mean, how did you even end up
in that accident?

00:14:56.612 --> 00:14:57.613 line:80%
[sighs]

00:14:58.823 --> 00:15:00.700 line:80%
-Did you drink and drive?
-No, I didn't.

00:15:00.783 --> 00:15:01.826 line:80%
I swear I didn't.

00:15:02.952 --> 00:15:06.205 line:80%
Then were you just speeding
for the thrill of it?

00:15:06.288 --> 00:15:07.581 line:80%
[sighs]

00:15:07.665 --> 00:15:09.208 line:80%
You think I'm some kind of lunatic?

00:15:09.291 --> 00:15:11.502 line:80%
Just randomly speeding
for the thrill of it?

00:15:13.212 --> 00:15:14.755 line:80%
The car just took off.

00:15:15.673 --> 00:15:17.466 line:80%
The brakes and all weren't working.

00:15:18.884 --> 00:15:19.885 line:80%
What in the world…

00:15:21.470 --> 00:15:25.057 line:80%
Then I'll first prepare a press release
with the dashcam footage.

00:15:25.641 --> 00:15:27.601 line:80%
-You can't.
-Why not?

00:15:27.685 --> 00:15:29.520 line:80%
You just can't.

00:15:33.065 --> 00:15:34.650 line:80%
His Majesty was with me.

00:15:35.317 --> 00:15:36.318 line:80%
His Majesty?

00:15:37.319 --> 00:15:38.738 line:80%
As in His Majesty the King?

00:15:40.448 --> 00:15:42.324 line:80%
The investigation won't be public.

00:15:44.034 --> 00:15:45.453 line:80%
[♪ amusing music playing]

00:15:45.536 --> 00:15:48.205 line:80%
[exclaiming]

00:15:48.289 --> 00:15:49.290 line:80%
Damn it.

00:15:49.373 --> 00:15:50.708 line:80%
It just never ends!

00:15:51.959 --> 00:15:52.960 line:80%
[sighs]

00:15:55.045 --> 00:15:56.255 line:80%
Let's reconsider this.

00:15:57.256 --> 00:15:59.175 line:80%
-Reconsider what?
-This marriage.

00:15:59.258 --> 00:16:00.468 line:80%
Can't you just call it off?

00:16:01.177 --> 00:16:04.180 line:80%
You're seriously bringing that up now?

00:16:04.263 --> 00:16:07.475 line:80%
There has been nothing but trouble
since Prince I-AN entered your life.

00:16:07.558 --> 00:16:09.769 line:80%
Egged at your own door
over a little scandal.

00:16:09.852 --> 00:16:12.438 line:80%
One wrong turn in the palace
made you an arsonist.

00:16:12.521 --> 00:16:15.024 line:80%
And this time, you nearly died.

00:16:15.107 --> 00:16:17.318 line:80%
Grand Prince I-AN was the one
who saved me.

00:16:17.401 --> 00:16:19.111 line:80%
Wait, he was the one who saved you?

00:16:20.070 --> 00:16:22.114 line:80%
Why are you two so caught up in this?

00:16:22.823 --> 00:16:24.033 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:16:24.116 --> 00:16:26.660 line:80%
I mean, why are you two overdoing it?

00:16:26.744 --> 00:16:28.537 line:80%
You'll be divorced in three years anyway.

00:16:28.621 --> 00:16:29.747 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] "Divorced"?

00:16:29.830 --> 00:16:31.040 line:80%
-[gasps]
-[music ends]

00:16:32.541 --> 00:16:33.542 line:80%
Jeongwoo.

00:16:37.838 --> 00:16:38.923 line:80%
[sighs]

00:16:40.341 --> 00:16:42.802 line:80%
[birds chirping]

00:16:42.885 --> 00:16:44.094 line:80%
[groans]

00:16:53.020 --> 00:16:54.313 line:80%
Where did you pop out from?

00:16:54.939 --> 00:16:56.482 line:80%
Is your job fun?

00:16:57.316 --> 00:16:58.526 line:80%
Pardon?

00:16:58.609 --> 00:16:59.944 line:80%
Working at the palace.

00:17:00.569 --> 00:17:01.654 line:80%
Oh, the palace?

00:17:02.488 --> 00:17:03.489 line:80%
Well…

00:17:03.989 --> 00:17:06.408 line:80%
Why? Are you looking to work there too?

00:17:07.535 --> 00:17:08.536 line:80%
Wow.

00:17:10.746 --> 00:17:12.373 line:80%
When Ms. Seong moves into the palace…

00:17:17.002 --> 00:17:18.212 line:80%
I'll be following her.

00:17:22.424 --> 00:17:23.843 line:80%
[clattering]

00:17:26.262 --> 00:17:27.429 line:80%
So charismatic.

00:17:39.191 --> 00:17:40.442 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] You said it was genuine.

00:17:41.068 --> 00:17:42.403 line:80%
Was it all a lie?

00:17:42.486 --> 00:17:45.197 line:80%
I wouldn't go so far as to call it a lie…

00:17:45.281 --> 00:17:46.949 line:80%
[sighs] Seong Huiju.

00:17:47.032 --> 00:17:48.617 line:80%
It's like a marriage of convenience.

00:17:49.159 --> 00:17:50.661 line:80%
A simple exchange of services.

00:17:51.287 --> 00:17:53.122 line:80%
You know plenty of people like that.

00:17:53.205 --> 00:17:54.665 line:80%
Don't make a big deal out of it.

00:17:54.748 --> 00:17:56.041 line:80%
That's completely different.

00:17:56.625 --> 00:17:57.585 line:80%
How so?

00:17:57.668 --> 00:18:00.045 line:80%
Don't you know how dangerous
the palace can be?

00:18:00.671 --> 00:18:02.590 line:80%
-Even this accident--
-I'm fine.

00:18:04.008 --> 00:18:06.010 line:80%
You think I proposed without knowing that?

00:18:06.719 --> 00:18:07.803 line:80%
You proposed to him?

00:18:09.054 --> 00:18:11.682 line:80%
Yeah. I was rejected about three times.

00:18:13.017 --> 00:18:14.018 line:80%
[sighs]

00:18:19.523 --> 00:18:20.524 line:80%
Listen.

00:18:21.108 --> 00:18:22.902 line:80%
I have everything but status.

00:18:23.402 --> 00:18:25.321 line:80%
I have the money, talent, and ambition,

00:18:25.404 --> 00:18:27.197 line:80%
but status is the one thing I don't have.

00:18:27.698 --> 00:18:28.991 line:80%
If I just had that…

00:18:30.743 --> 00:18:32.620 line:80%
I mean, why can't I have that too?

00:18:32.703 --> 00:18:33.704 line:80%
Is that all?

00:18:33.787 --> 00:18:35.873 line:80%
[♪ pensive music playing]

00:18:37.958 --> 00:18:39.793 line:80%
The reason you want to marry him.

00:18:40.669 --> 00:18:42.087 line:80%
Is status all there is to it?

00:18:43.714 --> 00:18:45.215 line:80%
What else could there be?

00:18:47.051 --> 00:18:48.052 line:80%
[sighs]

00:18:58.479 --> 00:18:59.480 line:80%
Then do it with me.

00:19:00.814 --> 00:19:02.024 line:80%
Do what?

00:19:03.567 --> 00:19:05.653 line:80%
Just marry me instead.

00:19:08.948 --> 00:19:10.115 line:80%
[Yun] <i>That will not do.</i>

00:19:11.659 --> 00:19:14.328 line:80%
The Grand Prince, who had surgery,
is returning to the palace.

00:19:15.454 --> 00:19:17.081 line:80%
Then surely, the King should as well.

00:19:17.164 --> 00:19:18.832 line:80%
But, Your Majesty…

00:19:18.916 --> 00:19:20.668 line:80%
If the king remains out of sight,

00:19:20.751 --> 00:19:23.420 line:80%
the people will come to think
they do not need one.

00:19:26.256 --> 00:19:27.466 line:80%
Do you not agree?

00:19:29.593 --> 00:19:31.095 line:80%
I agree.

00:19:37.226 --> 00:19:39.812 line:80%
Your Royal Highness, I've been discharged…

00:19:39.895 --> 00:19:40.896 line:80%
Huh?

00:19:45.025 --> 00:19:46.777 line:80%
Has he already been discharged?

00:19:49.947 --> 00:19:52.783 line:80%
[birds chirping]

00:19:52.866 --> 00:19:55.577 line:80%
[Lady Choi] Your Royal Highness,
Prime Minister Min has arrived.

00:19:56.078 --> 00:19:58.414 line:80%
[♪ pensive music playing]

00:19:58.497 --> 00:19:59.581 line:80%
Show him in.

00:20:03.627 --> 00:20:04.628 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:20:06.505 --> 00:20:07.548 line:80%
You are all dismissed.

00:20:20.894 --> 00:20:21.895 line:80%
[door closes]

00:20:26.483 --> 00:20:27.860 line:80%
[line ringing]

00:20:30.696 --> 00:20:31.697 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:20:31.780 --> 00:20:32.865 line:80%
I mean,

00:20:33.407 --> 00:20:37.619 line:80%
he should at least tell me
if he's been discharged.

00:20:38.495 --> 00:20:40.914 line:80%
-Not a great sign for married life.
-[line ringing]

00:20:42.374 --> 00:20:44.293 line:80%
He didn't say anything at the hospital?

00:20:44.793 --> 00:20:45.794 line:80%
When?

00:20:46.336 --> 00:20:48.756 line:80%
The last time I saw him
was early this morning.

00:20:49.298 --> 00:20:50.299 line:80%
What?

00:20:52.760 --> 00:20:54.428 line:80%
[♪ slow instrumental music playing]

00:21:02.227 --> 00:21:04.188 line:80%
[Hyejeong] <i>But he was standing</i>
<i>outside your room earlier.</i>

00:21:04.271 --> 00:21:06.857 line:80%
My room? When?

00:21:06.940 --> 00:21:08.859 line:80%
When Prime Minister Min stopped by.

00:21:10.027 --> 00:21:11.361 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>Then do it with me.</i>

00:21:11.445 --> 00:21:13.739 line:80%
<i>Just marry me instead.</i>

00:21:13.822 --> 00:21:14.907 line:80%
[♪ tense music plays]

00:21:14.990 --> 00:21:17.034 line:80%
-[screams]
-[gasps]

00:21:19.912 --> 00:21:21.246 line:80%
[exclaims]

00:21:21.914 --> 00:21:24.666 line:80%
[scoffs] Huh?

00:21:26.376 --> 00:21:28.003 line:80%
So what you're saying is

00:21:28.087 --> 00:21:31.256 line:80%
Ms. Seong was kicked out
by His Royal Highness?

00:21:31.340 --> 00:21:34.301 line:80%
Well, I mean, it was more like…

00:21:35.094 --> 00:21:36.470 line:80%
He asked that you return home.

00:21:36.553 --> 00:21:38.597 line:80%
That's the same thing!

00:21:38.680 --> 00:21:40.557 line:80%
[♪ dramatic music playing]

00:21:42.017 --> 00:21:43.268 line:80%
[sighs]

00:21:43.352 --> 00:21:44.436 line:80%
PRINCE

00:21:44.520 --> 00:21:46.063 line:80%
Is he kidding me right now?

00:21:46.146 --> 00:21:48.398 line:80%
-[line ringing]
-[sighs]

00:21:50.692 --> 00:21:51.693 line:80%
[groans]

00:21:53.987 --> 00:21:56.448 line:80%
Your Ladyship! Wait, Your Ladyship.

00:21:58.408 --> 00:21:59.409 line:80%
It's fine.

00:22:00.160 --> 00:22:02.037 line:80%
The master of the house
has already spoken.

00:22:03.038 --> 00:22:04.331 line:80%
It's not that.

00:22:06.959 --> 00:22:07.960 line:80%
The <i>hopae</i>.

00:22:09.169 --> 00:22:10.337 line:80%
He would like it returned.

00:22:18.095 --> 00:22:19.096 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:22:20.639 --> 00:22:21.974 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:22:30.649 --> 00:22:31.650 line:80%
[sighs]

00:22:32.943 --> 00:22:34.570 line:80%
[Huiju straining]

00:22:48.208 --> 00:22:49.710 line:80%
[music ends]

00:22:49.793 --> 00:22:52.087 line:80%
[crickets chirping]

00:22:52.171 --> 00:22:53.922 line:80%
[phone buzzing]

00:22:58.051 --> 00:23:01.221 line:80%
JUNIOR ALUM

00:23:04.683 --> 00:23:07.561 line:80%
[♪ melancholy music playing]

00:23:13.233 --> 00:23:14.234 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] Is that all?

00:23:16.111 --> 00:23:18.155 line:80%
The reason you want to marry him.

00:23:18.780 --> 00:23:20.073 line:80%
Is status all there is to it?

00:23:20.616 --> 00:23:21.783 line:80%
[Huiju] What else could there be?

00:23:22.534 --> 00:23:23.785 line:80%
Then do it with me.

00:23:25.162 --> 00:23:27.289 line:80%
Just marry me instead.

00:23:43.222 --> 00:23:44.223 line:80%
[phone buzzes]

00:23:46.683 --> 00:23:48.060 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>Say it to my face.</i>

00:23:48.977 --> 00:23:49.978 line:80%
<i>Whatever it is.</i>

00:23:55.692 --> 00:23:57.694 line:80%
[birds chirping]

00:24:12.751 --> 00:24:14.002 line:80%
[door closes]

00:24:25.514 --> 00:24:29.226 line:80%
It is a relief that
I will never have to teach you.

00:24:30.894 --> 00:24:32.896 line:80%
[♪ tense music playing]

00:24:33.605 --> 00:24:35.774 line:80%
No matter how great a teacher may be,

00:24:36.275 --> 00:24:39.778 line:80%
there are things
that simply cannot be taught.

00:24:44.157 --> 00:24:45.325 line:80%
Pardon?

00:24:55.544 --> 00:24:56.545 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:24:56.628 --> 00:25:00.048 line:80%
[Lady Choi] Your Royal Highness,
Ms. Seong Huiju has arrived.

00:25:01.883 --> 00:25:03.427 line:80%
[Huiju] Are you cleared to be out already?

00:25:06.722 --> 00:25:07.723 line:80%
That's your concern?

00:25:13.437 --> 00:25:15.022 line:80%
Why did you kick me out?

00:25:16.064 --> 00:25:17.357 line:80%
Because of the Queen Mother?

00:25:21.695 --> 00:25:22.696 line:80%
Or…

00:25:23.780 --> 00:25:24.906 line:80%
because of Jeongwoo?

00:25:26.533 --> 00:25:27.534 line:80%
What about him?

00:25:30.037 --> 00:25:31.705 line:80%
Didn't you overhear something?

00:25:31.788 --> 00:25:32.873 line:80%
What?

00:25:34.041 --> 00:25:35.042 line:80%
Never mind.

00:25:36.752 --> 00:25:38.879 line:80%
Then why did you kick me out?

00:25:38.962 --> 00:25:41.673 line:80%
I need to know what's going on
before I play along or not.

00:25:44.426 --> 00:25:46.011 line:80%
Someone messed with your car.

00:25:47.346 --> 00:25:48.805 line:80%
That is what caused the accident.

00:25:52.684 --> 00:25:53.810 line:80%
Who?

00:25:54.478 --> 00:25:55.520 line:80%
It's being investigated.

00:25:56.563 --> 00:25:57.689 line:80%
We will catch them.

00:26:00.150 --> 00:26:01.151 line:80%
And so,

00:26:02.694 --> 00:26:04.071 line:80%
I'm changing the plan.

00:26:04.154 --> 00:26:06.573 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:26:07.574 --> 00:26:08.575 line:80%
Let's…

00:26:12.829 --> 00:26:13.872 line:80%
call off this marriage.

00:26:19.586 --> 00:26:21.797 line:80%
What… What was that?

00:26:24.216 --> 00:26:26.301 line:80%
Call what off now?

00:26:28.136 --> 00:26:29.137 line:80%
The marriage.

00:26:31.723 --> 00:26:32.933 line:80%
But why?

00:26:33.683 --> 00:26:35.310 line:80%
Did Queen Mother tell you to do that?

00:26:35.394 --> 00:26:36.978 line:80%
Because of the accident?

00:26:37.062 --> 00:26:39.189 line:80%
That was because
His Majesty was relentless.

00:26:39.815 --> 00:26:42.109 line:80%
And you said someone messed with my car.

00:26:42.192 --> 00:26:44.152 line:80%
That makes me a victim too.

00:26:44.236 --> 00:26:45.237 line:80%
Exactly.

00:26:46.988 --> 00:26:48.365 line:80%
That's why we must call it off.

00:26:51.868 --> 00:26:53.829 line:80%
If I married someone like you

00:26:54.704 --> 00:26:56.957 line:80%
who breaks every rule
and has enemies at every turn…

00:26:59.459 --> 00:27:01.336 line:80%
the Crown is bound to fall.

00:27:16.226 --> 00:27:17.227 line:80%
[music ends]

00:27:17.310 --> 00:27:20.105 line:80%
[crickets chirping]

00:27:20.188 --> 00:27:23.733 line:80%
Father, this is a serious accident.

00:27:23.817 --> 00:27:25.152 line:80%
See here.

00:27:25.235 --> 00:27:27.946 line:80%
God, she's even driving
on the other side of the road.

00:27:28.029 --> 00:27:30.240 line:80%
If you ask me, at best, she's drunk.

00:27:30.323 --> 00:27:32.784 line:80%
At worst, it's hard drugs.
Nowadays, there's this…

00:27:34.327 --> 00:27:35.328 line:80%
Right.

00:27:35.412 --> 00:27:38.373 line:80%
I mean, she's always been
desperate for attention.

00:27:38.457 --> 00:27:42.002 line:80%
Now that she's dating Prince I-AN,
she's become a total hot tomato.

00:27:42.085 --> 00:27:43.128 line:80%
-And…
-Potato.

00:27:44.296 --> 00:27:46.590 line:80%
It's "hot potato."
Like a freshly baked hot potato.

00:27:46.673 --> 00:27:48.091 line:80%
Oh, right. Potato.

00:27:48.592 --> 00:27:49.718 line:80%
So, now…

00:27:50.302 --> 00:27:51.678 line:80%
Babe, does that matter?

00:27:51.761 --> 00:27:53.555 line:80%
Tomato. Potato. Same difference.

00:27:54.097 --> 00:27:55.182 line:80%
Sometimes, you can be…

00:27:55.891 --> 00:28:00.854 line:80%
Anyway, Father, this is totally
a huge, glaring owner-related risk.

00:28:00.937 --> 00:28:03.356 line:80%
You saw how the stock
had shot up over the last few days

00:28:03.440 --> 00:28:05.150 line:80%
and just took a nosedive, didn't you?

00:28:05.233 --> 00:28:07.444 line:80%
At this rate, Castle Beauty will just…

00:28:08.862 --> 00:28:10.113 line:80%
So what?

00:28:11.531 --> 00:28:12.949 line:80%
[sighs]

00:28:13.033 --> 00:28:14.576 line:80%
You want to take over Beauty?

00:28:14.659 --> 00:28:16.703 line:80%
Is that any way to speak to your brother?
[clicks tongue]

00:28:17.329 --> 00:28:18.997 line:80%
[sighs] What is it?

00:28:19.080 --> 00:28:20.916 line:80%
Let's make this quick. I'm busy.

00:28:23.335 --> 00:28:24.669 line:80%
Explain yourself.

00:28:26.880 --> 00:28:28.673 line:80%
What is there to explain?

00:28:29.633 --> 00:28:30.926 line:80%
It's just as you see.

00:28:31.009 --> 00:28:32.594 line:80%
Can you handle the consequences?

00:28:33.094 --> 00:28:34.763 line:80%
We'll issue a press release soon.

00:28:36.139 --> 00:28:37.140 line:80%
Neither alcohol

00:28:38.058 --> 00:28:39.559 line:80%
nor drugs were involved.

00:28:39.643 --> 00:28:41.603 line:80%
I heard they moved all your things

00:28:42.395 --> 00:28:43.897 line:80%
out of his house today.

00:28:44.564 --> 00:28:46.399 line:80%
Did you have me followed?

00:28:46.483 --> 00:28:48.068 line:80%
Explain yourself first!

00:28:48.151 --> 00:28:49.569 line:80%
[sighs]

00:28:51.780 --> 00:28:53.573 line:80%
It's just a lovers' spat.

00:28:54.866 --> 00:28:55.867 line:80%
Satisfied?

00:28:55.951 --> 00:28:57.452 line:80%
You call yourself a businesswoman,

00:28:57.536 --> 00:28:59.621 line:80%
yet you don't even realize
you're being used.

00:28:59.704 --> 00:29:02.082 line:80%
The Grand Prince has used you
for all you're worth.

00:29:03.500 --> 00:29:07.045 line:80%
He acted like he was above status,
as if he had no ambition for the throne.

00:29:07.837 --> 00:29:09.798 line:80%
Now that he has everything…

00:29:12.801 --> 00:29:14.219 line:80%
he's tossing you out.

00:29:14.302 --> 00:29:16.555 line:80%
[♪ pensive music playing]

00:29:17.180 --> 00:29:18.181 line:80%
So what?

00:29:19.975 --> 00:29:21.268 line:80%
What's the issue?

00:29:23.228 --> 00:29:24.813 line:80%
Two can play that game.

00:29:26.356 --> 00:29:29.025 line:80%
Do you know how much our stock
has jumped at the news

00:29:29.818 --> 00:29:32.237 line:80%
of Castle Group's Seong Huiju
marrying into the royal family?

00:29:32.320 --> 00:29:35.031 line:80%
Hey, kid. It all tanked today.

00:29:35.115 --> 00:29:37.534 line:80%
It will bounce right back
after the press release, damn it.

00:29:40.704 --> 00:29:41.705 line:80%
[sighs]

00:29:41.788 --> 00:29:44.791 line:80%
They're even asking if the "Castle" name
was part of some grand plan.

00:29:45.458 --> 00:29:46.459 line:80%
Haven't you seen the news?

00:29:46.543 --> 00:29:49.337 line:80%
Did it ever cross your mind that
it'll put a bigger target on our backs?

00:29:49.421 --> 00:29:51.006 line:80%
So we take a few hits!

00:29:52.882 --> 00:29:54.384 line:80%
A few hits won't kill you.

00:29:54.467 --> 00:29:55.552 line:80%
[sighs]

00:29:56.553 --> 00:29:57.554 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:29:58.221 --> 00:30:00.098 line:80%
And even if it did, what of it?

00:30:01.600 --> 00:30:03.059 line:80%
We all end up dead anyway.

00:30:03.852 --> 00:30:05.895 line:80%
What, do you plan to live forever?

00:30:07.188 --> 00:30:09.232 line:80%
Next time, just text me instead.

00:30:10.483 --> 00:30:13.486 line:80%
If you want to yell that badly,
then feel free to call.

00:30:16.948 --> 00:30:18.825 line:80%
-Sit down.
-I have plans.

00:30:18.908 --> 00:30:19.909 line:80%
Seong Huiju!

00:30:23.913 --> 00:30:24.914 line:80%
It's me.

00:30:25.457 --> 00:30:27.334 line:80%
I need you to look into something for me.

00:30:38.595 --> 00:30:40.221 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>Find out who last worked</i>
<i>on my car.</i>

00:30:40.764 --> 00:30:41.765 line:80%
[sighs]

00:30:42.474 --> 00:30:46.102 line:80%
<i>Dig up everything</i>
<i>you possibly can on them.</i>

00:30:50.690 --> 00:30:51.691 line:80%
[Hyeon sighs]

00:30:52.192 --> 00:30:53.943 line:80%
A grand prince of this nation can't…

00:30:55.570 --> 00:30:57.530 line:80%
break an engagement.

00:30:58.073 --> 00:31:01.326 line:80%
Technically, there's nothing to break.
We were never engaged.

00:31:01.409 --> 00:31:02.410 line:80%
Are you kidding?

00:31:02.494 --> 00:31:05.455 line:80%
After all that talk
about getting married and living together?

00:31:05.538 --> 00:31:06.706 line:80%
We never lived together.

00:31:06.790 --> 00:31:08.875 line:80%
-I was at the palace, and she was--
-Listen.

00:31:10.960 --> 00:31:14.255 line:80%
Even if you killed someone,
I would take your side.

00:31:14.339 --> 00:31:15.674 line:80%
But this is not cool. It's--

00:31:16.841 --> 00:31:18.718 line:80%
Why would you side with a murderer?

00:31:20.136 --> 00:31:22.013 line:80%
You must've had your reasons.

00:31:22.931 --> 00:31:24.933 line:80%
So, why did you break it off?

00:31:25.016 --> 00:31:27.102 line:80%
-I didn't "break"--
-Seriously? Come on.

00:31:27.894 --> 00:31:29.104 line:80%
That's not what I'm asking.

00:31:31.940 --> 00:31:33.817 line:80%
Why did you break it off?

00:31:40.281 --> 00:31:42.283 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:31:44.160 --> 00:31:45.161 line:80%
To keep her alive.

00:31:48.373 --> 00:31:51.543 line:20%
[young I-AN] <i>Mother, should we pick up</i>
<i>fried chicken on the way to the palace?</i>

00:31:51.626 --> 00:31:52.627 line:80%
Fried chicken?

00:31:52.711 --> 00:31:55.004 line:80%
Hwan texted and said he wanted some.

00:31:56.506 --> 00:31:58.508 line:80%
He's always making me do stuff like this.

00:31:58.591 --> 00:32:01.052 line:80%
[chuckles] Shall we, then?

00:32:01.678 --> 00:32:02.679 line:80%
Yes, Mother.

00:32:04.556 --> 00:32:05.557 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:32:23.074 --> 00:32:24.409 line:80%
[gasps]

00:32:29.122 --> 00:32:30.540 line:80%
Mother!

00:32:39.466 --> 00:32:42.135 line:80%
[sobbing]

00:33:00.195 --> 00:33:03.072 line:80%
[young I-AN] <i>Mother, should we pick up</i>
<i>fried chicken on the way to the palace?</i>

00:33:04.949 --> 00:33:06.201 line:80%
[Uihyeon] <i>Shall we, then?</i>

00:33:12.415 --> 00:33:13.625 line:80%
[sobbing]

00:33:13.708 --> 00:33:15.251 line:80%
-[young I-AN] <i>Mother…</i>
-[breathing heavily]

00:33:16.419 --> 00:33:17.629 line:80%
<i>Mother…</i>

00:33:22.926 --> 00:33:25.136 line:80%
[breathing heavily, sighs]

00:33:25.220 --> 00:33:27.305 line:80%
[♪ sorrowful music playing]

00:33:48.409 --> 00:33:50.370 line:80%
[engine revving]

00:33:53.289 --> 00:33:54.916 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>There wasn't a doubt in my mind.</i>

00:33:55.583 --> 00:33:58.461 line:80%
<i>It was a moment</i>
<i>I'd regretted countless times.</i>

00:34:01.130 --> 00:34:03.132 line:80%
[tires screeching]

00:34:14.102 --> 00:34:15.395 line:80%
That's what changed my mind.

00:34:17.814 --> 00:34:19.065 line:80%
[Hyeon] It was just an accident.

00:34:19.983 --> 00:34:22.151 line:80%
It wasn't even your fault, so why?

00:34:24.863 --> 00:34:25.905 line:80%
It was my fault.

00:34:28.032 --> 00:34:29.325 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>Signs of deliberate tampering</i>

00:34:29.909 --> 00:34:31.619 line:80%
were found in the accident vehicle.

00:34:33.037 --> 00:34:36.541 line:80%
We'll need to investigate further
to determine if they were targeting

00:34:37.083 --> 00:34:38.543 line:80%
His Majesty or Ms. Seong.

00:34:42.881 --> 00:34:45.508 line:80%
However, do not concern yourself too much.

00:34:47.468 --> 00:34:49.304 line:80%
I will do everything
in my power to protect

00:34:49.387 --> 00:34:50.847 line:80%
His Majesty, Your Royal Highness,

00:34:52.140 --> 00:34:53.308 line:80%
and the Crown.

00:34:56.936 --> 00:34:57.937 line:80%
In turn,

00:34:58.563 --> 00:34:59.647 line:80%
I'd like to ask you

00:35:01.524 --> 00:35:03.943 line:80%
to protect Ms. Seong Huiju.

00:35:06.237 --> 00:35:08.323 line:80%
Please cast her far away from the palace.

00:35:10.116 --> 00:35:12.869 line:80%
I sincerely implore you,
Your Royal Highness.

00:35:18.625 --> 00:35:19.751 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>That is why</i>

00:35:21.002 --> 00:35:22.128 line:80%
I must step aside.

00:35:24.213 --> 00:35:25.214 line:80%
Your Royal Highness.

00:35:25.757 --> 00:35:26.841 line:80%
Thus,

00:35:28.384 --> 00:35:29.427 line:80%
I want to do something.

00:35:30.637 --> 00:35:31.638 line:80%
Pardon?

00:35:33.306 --> 00:35:34.307 line:80%
A parting gift.

00:35:36.100 --> 00:35:37.101 line:80%
For her.

00:35:43.441 --> 00:35:44.692 line:80%
[sighs]

00:35:45.360 --> 00:35:47.362 line:80%
[birds chirping]

00:35:48.529 --> 00:35:50.114 line:80%
[Im] The Inner Court Banquet guest list,

00:35:50.198 --> 00:35:51.783 line:20%
proposed by the Royal Secretariat.

00:35:51.866 --> 00:35:54.160 line:20%
PALACE EVENT HOSTED
FOR LADIES OF THE INNER COURT

00:35:54.243 --> 00:35:56.120 line:20%
TRADITIONALLY HELD
SINCE THE JOSEON DYNASTY

00:35:58.164 --> 00:36:00.500 line:80%
Remove the scandal-ridden figures.

00:36:04.295 --> 00:36:05.505 line:80%
No new money either.

00:36:07.924 --> 00:36:10.051 line:80%
The merits of these two are comparable.

00:36:10.134 --> 00:36:12.053 line:80%
Bring me the details of their families.

00:36:12.136 --> 00:36:13.388 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:36:13.471 --> 00:36:15.390 line:80%
Your standards rise every year.

00:36:16.265 --> 00:36:19.602 line:80%
The more exclusive the guest list,

00:36:19.686 --> 00:36:22.563 line:80%
the deeper the despair of the uninvited.

00:36:23.606 --> 00:36:27.151 line:80%
And with it comes
the greater delight of those invited.

00:36:28.194 --> 00:36:29.612 line:80%
INNER COURT BANQUET GUEST LIST

00:36:31.030 --> 00:36:32.031 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:36:32.532 --> 00:36:34.784 line:80%
Another gathering
of the usual suspects this year.

00:36:34.867 --> 00:36:35.952 line:80%
All nobility.

00:36:36.035 --> 00:36:37.620 line:80%
The competition is fiercer every year.

00:36:38.246 --> 00:36:39.956 line:80%
It does offer many benefits.

00:36:40.039 --> 00:36:41.416 line:80%
[secretary] That is true.

00:36:41.499 --> 00:36:43.418 line:80%
But if they managed to secure an invite,

00:36:43.501 --> 00:36:46.254 line:80%
they must already possess
plenty of money and land.

00:36:46.337 --> 00:36:48.506 line:80%
[♪ triumphant music playing]

00:36:48.589 --> 00:36:51.384 line:80%
That's precisely why they're willing
to die for royal prestige.

00:36:52.051 --> 00:36:54.095 line:80%
It's the only thing their money can't buy.

00:36:58.975 --> 00:37:00.184 line:80%
[staff member] Ma'am.

00:37:00.268 --> 00:37:02.979 line:80%
I had to jump through
some pretty high hoops to secure

00:37:03.062 --> 00:37:05.231 line:80%
this Inner Court Banquet guest list.

00:37:05.314 --> 00:37:06.899 line:80%
A lot of familiar faces, right?

00:37:06.983 --> 00:37:09.402 line:80%
A gathering of female business leaders
in their thirties…

00:37:09.485 --> 00:37:11.320 line:80%
[Huiju] Still just 20 of them, right?

00:37:11.404 --> 00:37:13.823 line:80%
Not even enough for a soccer match.

00:37:13.906 --> 00:37:15.450 line:80%
But, ma'am, you said so yourself.

00:37:15.533 --> 00:37:17.952 line:80%
"One absolute is worth
more than a hundred maybes."

00:37:18.036 --> 00:37:19.579 line:80%
These are 20 absolutes.

00:37:19.662 --> 00:37:21.414 line:80%
All backed by the Crown, no less!

00:37:22.874 --> 00:37:24.042 line:80%
[sighs]

00:37:25.501 --> 00:37:28.254 line:80%
You once called this
the most luxurious marketing strategy…

00:37:28.337 --> 00:37:30.298 line:80%
So what's your point?

00:37:30.381 --> 00:37:31.841 line:80%
Moving on.

00:37:31.924 --> 00:37:34.844 line:80%
Since you have ties
with the palace and all, we thought

00:37:34.927 --> 00:37:37.513 line:80%
one of the guests could be
a new face of our luxury line.

00:37:37.597 --> 00:37:38.556 line:80%
Yes, so we…

00:37:39.057 --> 00:37:40.641 line:80%
Just a moment. Oh.

00:37:45.354 --> 00:37:46.647 line:80%
Hello.

00:37:47.398 --> 00:37:48.399 line:80%
Hello.

00:37:49.609 --> 00:37:52.612 line:20%
MS. SEONG HUIJU, YOU ARE CORDIALLY INVITED
TO THE INNER COURT BANQUET

00:37:52.695 --> 00:37:53.905 line:20%
[Huiju exclaims]

00:37:53.988 --> 00:37:55.364 line:80%
Me?

00:37:55.448 --> 00:37:56.783 line:80%
Yes, Ms. Seong.

00:37:58.493 --> 00:38:02.914 line:80%
The Inner Court Banquet
is a very important annual event.

00:38:02.997 --> 00:38:05.541 line:80%
Of course, I'm aware
of the Inner Court Banquet.

00:38:06.501 --> 00:38:10.630 line:80%
But I thought only noblewomen
were invited to this.

00:38:10.713 --> 00:38:13.257 line:80%
What? No such criterion exists…

00:38:13.341 --> 00:38:14.634 line:80%
It certainly doesn't,

00:38:14.717 --> 00:38:16.094 line:80%
but that's how it's been done.

00:38:16.928 --> 00:38:19.138 line:80%
For 600 years, without a single exception.

00:38:23.309 --> 00:38:26.604 line:80%
The thing about change is that
it happens gradually…

00:38:26.687 --> 00:38:27.772 line:80%
So? How? Why?

00:38:27.855 --> 00:38:31.067 line:80%
Why have I suddenly been invited?

00:38:31.567 --> 00:38:35.071 line:80%
Yes, well, you've experienced
some hardships recently,

00:38:35.154 --> 00:38:38.658 line:80%
and the press release
about your breakup is about to go out.

00:38:39.158 --> 00:38:42.411 line:80%
So to make it clear the palace
wasn't responsible for your breakup…

00:38:42.495 --> 00:38:45.248 line:80%
You want to stage a performance
for the public?

00:38:45.331 --> 00:38:47.667 line:80%
[laughing]

00:38:50.461 --> 00:38:51.462 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:38:54.507 --> 00:38:55.883 line:80%
Yes, you see,

00:38:55.967 --> 00:38:58.177 line:80%
the dress codes
for the two parts are different.

00:38:58.261 --> 00:39:00.429 line:80%
It's customary to wear
a <i>dangui</i> for the reception.

00:39:00.513 --> 00:39:03.891 line:80%
The Queen Mother will wear white,
so it's best to avoid that color.

00:39:03.975 --> 00:39:05.560 line:80%
No thanks.

00:39:05.643 --> 00:39:08.020 line:80%
To what exactly? The <i>dangui</i>?

00:39:09.230 --> 00:39:10.982 line:80%
[sighs] The Inner Court Banquet.

00:39:13.901 --> 00:39:15.027 line:80%
Ms. Seong.

00:39:15.111 --> 00:39:16.279 line:80%
Why?

00:39:16.362 --> 00:39:18.489 line:80%
The Inner Court Banquet?
You don't want to attend?

00:39:19.073 --> 00:39:20.324 line:80%
[laughs]

00:39:20.408 --> 00:39:23.161 line:80%
Silly me, how did I forget
to mention this?

00:39:23.244 --> 00:39:27.540 line:80%
Attending it once will lead
to many more royal invitations.

00:39:27.623 --> 00:39:30.209 line:80%
Even royal patronage
for your overseas business.

00:39:30.293 --> 00:39:31.878 line:80%
Okay. Above all else,

00:39:32.378 --> 00:39:35.840 line:80%
this will confirm that you two
didn't end things badly,

00:39:35.923 --> 00:39:38.634 line:80%
and that you remain
on good terms with the Crown.

00:39:38.718 --> 00:39:40.887 line:80%
We can pivot
to an "it's all cool" narrative--

00:39:40.970 --> 00:39:42.513 line:80%
-That would be excellent.
-Mm-hmm.

00:39:42.597 --> 00:39:44.056 line:80%
You've always wanted an invite.

00:39:44.140 --> 00:39:46.934 line:80%
That was before marriage was on the table.

00:39:48.352 --> 00:39:49.604 line:80%
-No thanks.
-[sighs]

00:39:49.687 --> 00:39:52.523 line:80%
But still, His Royal Highness personally…

00:39:52.607 --> 00:39:53.774 line:80%
No…

00:39:54.567 --> 00:39:55.860 line:80%
thank…

00:39:58.029 --> 00:39:59.030 line:80%
you.

00:40:00.990 --> 00:40:02.074 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>What?</i>

00:40:02.158 --> 00:40:04.076 line:80%
So? You just left?

00:40:04.160 --> 00:40:08.247 line:80%
What choice did I have? She was about
to murder me in broad daylight.

00:40:10.875 --> 00:40:11.876 line:80%
[sighs]

00:40:13.002 --> 00:40:15.588 line:80%
I heard you moved Seong Huiju
out of your private residence.

00:40:17.757 --> 00:40:19.133 line:80%
What are you playing at?

00:40:20.676 --> 00:40:21.928 line:80%
I am protecting her.

00:40:23.304 --> 00:40:24.597 line:80%
Her ties to the Crown

00:40:25.640 --> 00:40:27.099 line:80%
have only led her to misfortune.

00:40:27.183 --> 00:40:28.392 line:80%
Then,

00:40:29.477 --> 00:40:31.562 line:80%
ensure she no longer has any ties
to the Crown.

00:40:32.563 --> 00:40:33.648 line:80%
That is my intention.

00:40:37.735 --> 00:40:38.778 line:80%
I will not pursue

00:40:40.279 --> 00:40:41.489 line:80%
marriage with Seong Huiju.

00:40:42.615 --> 00:40:43.616 line:80%
In turn,

00:40:44.116 --> 00:40:46.244 line:80%
I ask that you invite her
to the Inner Court Banquet.

00:40:47.453 --> 00:40:48.829 line:80%
I do not wish to see her suffer

00:40:49.580 --> 00:40:51.040 line:80%
because of our parting.

00:40:56.796 --> 00:40:57.922 line:80%
Summon her to the palace.

00:40:58.839 --> 00:41:00.091 line:80%
Ms. Seong Huiju?

00:41:00.591 --> 00:41:01.592 line:80%
You want me to?

00:41:03.177 --> 00:41:06.180 line:80%
I shall persuade her myself.

00:41:07.306 --> 00:41:08.349 line:80%
[Huiju] <i>No thanks.</i>

00:41:10.101 --> 00:41:11.394 line:80%
No, thank you.

00:41:12.770 --> 00:41:14.272 line:80%
Who is he to summon me?

00:41:15.398 --> 00:41:17.066 line:80%
-[sighs]
-[knocks on door]

00:41:17.942 --> 00:41:19.694 line:80%
[gasps] Is the fried chicken here?

00:41:20.444 --> 00:41:22.989 line:80%
What? You ordered fried chicken again?

00:41:26.450 --> 00:41:27.827 line:80%
You open it.

00:41:36.419 --> 00:41:37.545 line:80%
Mmm.

00:41:38.129 --> 00:41:40.464 line:80%
People have nothing
on fried chicken, right?

00:41:40.548 --> 00:41:42.550 line:80%
It shows up right on time
when you call them.

00:41:42.633 --> 00:41:44.260 line:80%
You never get sick of it.

00:41:44.802 --> 00:41:46.012 line:80%
Always so reliable.

00:41:47.471 --> 00:41:48.681 line:80%
-Wait…
-What?

00:41:49.307 --> 00:41:51.058 line:80%
Are you upset you got dumped?

00:41:53.311 --> 00:41:55.688 line:80%
Why would you say that
when I'm enjoying fried chicken?

00:41:56.230 --> 00:41:57.231 line:80%
I'm done.

00:41:59.317 --> 00:42:01.319 line:80%
Oh, I mean…

00:42:02.862 --> 00:42:05.614 line:80%
Why are you so upset?

00:42:06.115 --> 00:42:07.908 line:80%
It was all pretend.

00:42:09.076 --> 00:42:11.454 line:80%
That's exactly why.

00:42:12.997 --> 00:42:15.124 line:80%
Relationships end
when one side loses interest,

00:42:15.207 --> 00:42:16.667 line:80%
whether the other likes it or not.

00:42:16.751 --> 00:42:18.294 line:80%
But that's not what this was.

00:42:18.377 --> 00:42:20.212 line:80%
This was strictly a contract.

00:42:22.214 --> 00:42:23.591 line:80%
Father was right.

00:42:24.425 --> 00:42:27.928 line:80%
I'm a businesswoman. I should've known
better than to trust a stranger.

00:42:28.846 --> 00:42:30.514 line:80%
I should've drawn up a contract.

00:42:40.316 --> 00:42:42.318 line:80%
[♪ rock music playing]

00:42:42.401 --> 00:42:43.444 line:80%
Ms. Seong, the invite--

00:42:43.527 --> 00:42:44.779 line:80%
No thanks.

00:42:45.363 --> 00:42:46.364 line:80%
Ms. Seong.

00:42:46.906 --> 00:42:47.907 line:80%
No thanks.

00:42:47.990 --> 00:42:50.993 line:80%
-[Hyejeong] <i>You're really not going?</i>
-No, thank you!

00:42:56.207 --> 00:42:57.291 line:80%
Is she dumb?

00:42:57.375 --> 00:42:59.460 line:80%
Just give up already.

00:42:59.543 --> 00:43:01.379 line:80%
She doesn't want anything to do with you.

00:43:01.462 --> 00:43:02.755 line:80%
Choi Hyeon.

00:43:05.549 --> 00:43:07.009 line:80%
I mean, I can't blame her.

00:43:07.510 --> 00:43:09.845 line:80%
You dumped her
and now you're acting so uncool.

00:43:14.141 --> 00:43:16.477 line:80%
-[sighs]
-[siren wailing]

00:43:16.560 --> 00:43:17.853 line:80%
[Hyejeong] Hey, Ms. Seong.

00:43:17.937 --> 00:43:20.022 line:80%
I went to the repair shop and secured

00:43:20.106 --> 00:43:22.858 line:80%
the résumé of the bastard
who tampered with your car and fled.

00:43:23.567 --> 00:43:25.903 line:80%
They ran a search with his photo,

00:43:25.986 --> 00:43:28.489 line:80%
but he doesn't seem to have any priors.

00:43:29.281 --> 00:43:33.035 line:80%
[sighs] He must've bought
something there at least once.

00:43:33.619 --> 00:43:34.620 line:80%
<i>What?</i>

00:43:35.246 --> 00:43:37.373 line:80%
There's a convenience store
in front of the shop.

00:43:38.249 --> 00:43:39.625 line:80%
Oh, right.

00:43:39.708 --> 00:43:41.961 line:80%
Scour their CCTV footage.

00:43:42.044 --> 00:43:43.796 line:80%
I want his purchase history.

00:43:46.632 --> 00:43:47.716 line:80%
[sighs]

00:43:49.093 --> 00:43:50.094 line:80%
[phone buzzes]

00:43:52.138 --> 00:43:53.222 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>Say it to my face.</i>

00:43:54.223 --> 00:43:55.224 line:80%
<i>Whatever it is.</i>

00:43:56.392 --> 00:43:58.686 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:43:58.769 --> 00:44:00.104 line:80%
[sighs]

00:44:00.187 --> 00:44:02.606 line:80%
[birds chirping]

00:44:02.690 --> 00:44:03.941 line:80%
[cat purring]

00:44:14.452 --> 00:44:16.036 line:80%
Are you afraid to go to the banquet?

00:44:19.165 --> 00:44:21.250 line:80%
I will prepare everything you need.

00:44:22.543 --> 00:44:23.627 line:80%
From the clothes

00:44:24.295 --> 00:44:25.629 line:80%
to the etiquette lessons.

00:44:25.713 --> 00:44:27.006 line:80%
Why?

00:44:27.840 --> 00:44:31.760 line:80%
I break every rule
and have enemies at every turn.

00:44:32.761 --> 00:44:34.472 line:80%
-So why would I go there?
-Seong Huiju.

00:44:34.555 --> 00:44:36.599 line:80%
Then provide me with a convincing reason.

00:44:37.975 --> 00:44:40.811 line:80%
You risked your life to save me,
just to break off the engagement.

00:44:40.895 --> 00:44:43.397 line:80%
And now you're inviting me
to the Inner Court Banquet?

00:44:44.356 --> 00:44:45.524 line:80%
A split personality?

00:44:45.608 --> 00:44:47.026 line:80%
I am trying to protect you!

00:44:49.028 --> 00:44:50.196 line:80%
We're not even married…

00:44:52.781 --> 00:44:54.533 line:80%
and you've been attacked multiple times.

00:44:56.076 --> 00:44:57.620 line:80%
And once the breakup news breaks,

00:44:59.538 --> 00:45:00.956 line:80%
it'll only get worse.

00:45:01.832 --> 00:45:02.833 line:80%
So what?

00:45:04.168 --> 00:45:07.379 line:80%
"Social ascent is dangerous.
Be content with an invite to the banquet."

00:45:08.297 --> 00:45:10.549 line:80%
-Is that it?
-Just stay out of harm's way.

00:45:12.218 --> 00:45:13.385 line:80%
Is that so difficult?

00:45:14.178 --> 00:45:15.179 line:80%
[sighs]

00:45:16.722 --> 00:45:17.723 line:80%
Coward.

00:45:19.934 --> 00:45:21.060 line:80%
What?

00:45:21.143 --> 00:45:23.979 line:80%
[cat meows]

00:45:34.240 --> 00:45:36.116 line:80%
-What are you…
-You like cats.

00:45:37.952 --> 00:45:38.953 line:80%
Try protecting them.

00:45:39.954 --> 00:45:41.247 line:80%
I'm going to attack them.

00:45:48.420 --> 00:45:49.421 line:80%
[sighs]

00:45:50.506 --> 00:45:52.049 line:80%
What the hell are you doing?

00:46:01.517 --> 00:46:03.227 line:80%
This is how you protect someone.

00:46:04.687 --> 00:46:05.771 line:80%
You go on the offensive.

00:46:06.730 --> 00:46:08.023 line:80%
You fight back.

00:46:20.327 --> 00:46:22.162 line:80%
You never learned to bend.

00:46:22.246 --> 00:46:25.457 line:80%
You only know how to bend.
That's why you lose to people beneath you.

00:46:27.042 --> 00:46:28.586 line:80%
I asked you for status,

00:46:29.545 --> 00:46:31.839 line:80%
not a cozy cradle to hide from the world.

00:46:36.135 --> 00:46:37.344 line:80%
Do not bend to their will.

00:46:38.679 --> 00:46:39.972 line:80%
Do not back away

00:46:41.599 --> 00:46:42.933 line:80%
and do not compromise.

00:46:46.353 --> 00:46:47.980 line:80%
That's how you and I both

00:46:49.523 --> 00:46:50.858 line:80%
get what we want.

00:47:02.578 --> 00:47:03.954 line:80%
[Hyeon] She is one scary lady.

00:47:05.414 --> 00:47:07.958 line:80%
I know all's fair in love and war,

00:47:08.042 --> 00:47:09.585 line:80%
but isn't this taking it too far?

00:47:09.668 --> 00:47:11.462 line:80%
Is a "safe exit" an option here?

00:47:11.545 --> 00:47:13.380 line:80%
I told you I hurt myself.

00:47:13.464 --> 00:47:16.592 line:80%
Even so, how could she let
your precious body be injured?

00:47:16.675 --> 00:47:18.260 line:80%
She has crossed the line.

00:47:18.344 --> 00:47:19.345 line:80%
I told you she didn't.

00:47:21.388 --> 00:47:22.640 line:80%
[sighs]

00:47:24.266 --> 00:47:26.018 line:80%
She never released the arrow.

00:47:27.770 --> 00:47:28.854 line:80%
What?

00:47:28.937 --> 00:47:30.939 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:47:36.028 --> 00:47:37.029 line:80%
[sighs]

00:47:44.828 --> 00:47:46.038 line:80%
She never crossed the line.

00:47:51.794 --> 00:47:55.506 line:80%
-[employee groans] My eyes are fried.
-[sighs]

00:47:55.589 --> 00:47:57.091 line:80%
[employee 2] He must've been
super diligent.

00:47:57.174 --> 00:48:00.135 line:80%
Never going to the convenience store
across the street.

00:48:00.219 --> 00:48:01.345 line:80%
My thoughts exactly.

00:48:02.638 --> 00:48:03.889 line:80%
Wait.

00:48:04.473 --> 00:48:05.724 line:80%
I think this is him.

00:48:06.475 --> 00:48:07.476 line:80%
Take a look at this.

00:48:07.559 --> 00:48:09.061 line:80%
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

00:48:09.728 --> 00:48:11.772 line:80%
-It's him, right?
-[employee 3] Yeah, it is.

00:48:19.238 --> 00:48:20.322 line:80%
Castle Pay!

00:48:20.989 --> 00:48:22.116 line:80%
[exclaims]

00:48:22.199 --> 00:48:23.742 line:80%
-Yeah, he used Castle Pay!
-He did.

00:48:23.826 --> 00:48:25.494 line:80%
Good job!

00:48:25.577 --> 00:48:26.704 line:80%
Hold on.

00:48:26.787 --> 00:48:31.041 line:80%
But the CEO of Castle Card is
Senior Managing Director Seong, isn't it?

00:48:33.585 --> 00:48:35.546 line:80%
Let me get this straight.

00:48:35.629 --> 00:48:39.508 line:80%
You need help from your dear brother.

00:48:40.551 --> 00:48:42.386 line:80%
[sighs] Yes.

00:48:46.223 --> 00:48:47.266 line:80%
I mean, sure.

00:48:48.976 --> 00:48:50.477 line:80%
I could do that for you, but--

00:48:50.561 --> 00:48:51.854 line:80%
Who is he anyway?

00:48:53.021 --> 00:48:54.481 line:80%
He's trying to kill me.

00:48:57.735 --> 00:48:58.736 line:80%
This kid…

00:48:59.278 --> 00:49:01.864 line:80%
Do you take me for a sucker?

00:49:01.947 --> 00:49:02.990 line:80%
Are you serious?

00:49:04.241 --> 00:49:05.409 line:80%
[sighs]

00:49:06.243 --> 00:49:08.203 line:80%
So show me what you can do.

00:49:09.204 --> 00:49:11.081 line:80%
I want some vigilante justice.

00:49:11.165 --> 00:49:12.374 line:80%
This kid…

00:49:13.792 --> 00:49:15.210 line:80%
Who is this guy anyway?

00:49:19.715 --> 00:49:22.134 line:80%
[♪ gentle music playing]

00:49:35.272 --> 00:49:36.482 line:80%
[Jeongwoo] <i>Then do it with me.</i>

00:49:37.691 --> 00:49:39.735 line:80%
Just marry me instead.

00:49:50.579 --> 00:49:52.748 line:80%
Why would I marry you?

00:49:53.957 --> 00:49:54.958 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:49:59.254 --> 00:50:00.339 line:80%
Why not?

00:50:01.965 --> 00:50:03.467 line:80%
It's not like you have feelings

00:50:04.176 --> 00:50:05.636 line:80%
for either of us.

00:50:07.221 --> 00:50:08.639 line:80%
You have a five-year term.

00:50:09.932 --> 00:50:13.185 line:80%
It doesn't matter
if I mess up or divorce him.

00:50:13.268 --> 00:50:14.812 line:80%
He'll be a royal for life.

00:50:15.437 --> 00:50:16.605 line:80%
But you're different.

00:50:22.361 --> 00:50:23.737 line:80%
You should serve another term.

00:50:24.613 --> 00:50:25.906 line:80%
Pull yourself together.

00:50:37.084 --> 00:50:39.086 line:80%
[crickets chirping]

00:50:41.505 --> 00:50:43.507 line:80%
[music ends]

00:50:58.272 --> 00:50:59.773 line:80%
[Lady Choi] Is it weighing on your mind?

00:51:03.694 --> 00:51:05.153 line:80%
I heard from Aide Choi.

00:51:05.654 --> 00:51:08.156 line:80%
That there was an argument
at your private residence.

00:51:09.575 --> 00:51:11.577 line:80%
[sighs] Choi Hyeon…

00:51:12.369 --> 00:51:13.787 line:80%
He can be quite the chatterbox.

00:51:13.871 --> 00:51:16.164 line:80%
Just let her win if you can.

00:51:17.040 --> 00:51:18.917 line:80%
She is already under the cutting scrutiny

00:51:19.418 --> 00:51:20.878 line:80%
of the court of public opinion.

00:51:20.961 --> 00:51:23.380 line:80%
[♪ emotional music playing]

00:51:44.902 --> 00:51:46.904 line:80%
[phone buzzing]

00:51:48.363 --> 00:51:49.364 line:80%
[sighs]

00:51:49.448 --> 00:51:51.825 line:80%
PRINCE

00:52:03.337 --> 00:52:04.338 line:80%
Hello.

00:52:05.631 --> 00:52:07.132 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>The invitation</i>
<i>has already been sent.</i>

00:52:09.593 --> 00:52:10.761 line:80%
So you cannot decline.

00:52:15.724 --> 00:52:16.892 line:80%
[sighs]

00:52:18.685 --> 00:52:19.770 line:80%
It's for your sake.

00:52:22.689 --> 00:52:23.690 line:80%
I know.

00:52:25.984 --> 00:52:26.985 line:80%
[sighs]

00:52:33.575 --> 00:52:34.618 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:52:36.036 --> 00:52:38.622 line:80%
I never meant to hurt you.

00:52:40.707 --> 00:52:42.167 line:80%
Or the cat.

00:52:43.585 --> 00:52:44.586 line:80%
<i>I know.</i>

00:52:49.758 --> 00:52:50.759 line:80%
I'm sorry too.

00:52:51.760 --> 00:52:55.263 line:80%
[♪ indie music playing]

00:52:55.889 --> 00:52:57.140 line:80%
For not keeping my promise.

00:53:00.978 --> 00:53:02.062 line:80%
[sighs]

00:53:03.981 --> 00:53:05.107 line:80%
As long as you know.

00:53:18.286 --> 00:53:20.747 line:80%
CASTLE BEAUTY

00:53:22.708 --> 00:53:23.875 line:80%
-[music ends]
-[chuckles]

00:53:23.959 --> 00:53:25.127 line:80%
[slurping]

00:53:25.752 --> 00:53:26.753 line:80%
[sighs]

00:53:29.381 --> 00:53:31.550 line:80%
I heard you will be attending.

00:53:32.384 --> 00:53:36.388 line:80%
Yes, well, he just insisted
it would be in my best interest.

00:53:36.471 --> 00:53:38.098 line:80%
[chuckles]

00:53:38.181 --> 00:53:40.100 line:80%
There's one thing you should be aware of.

00:53:40.183 --> 00:53:42.060 line:80%
-Just a moment.
-Sure.

00:53:42.894 --> 00:53:44.479 line:80%
-Please continue.
-All right.

00:53:44.563 --> 00:53:48.400 line:80%
All the other invited guests
hold official rank.

00:53:48.984 --> 00:53:52.029 line:80%
In the royal court,
rank defines one's place in the hierarchy.

00:53:52.112 --> 00:53:54.531 line:80%
-Hierarchy?
-Yes. Uh…

00:53:55.115 --> 00:53:59.453 line:80%
I'm sure you noticed
after attending a few royal events.

00:53:59.536 --> 00:54:01.621 line:80%
When you're with someone of a higher rank,

00:54:01.705 --> 00:54:05.584 line:80%
you must walk behind them.
That's the custom.

00:54:10.922 --> 00:54:12.007 line:80%
I'll keep that in mind.

00:54:12.507 --> 00:54:13.633 line:80%
[sighs]

00:54:13.717 --> 00:54:15.010 line:80%
Thank you.

00:54:15.093 --> 00:54:16.261 line:80%
And there's this.

00:54:17.554 --> 00:54:18.597 line:80%
Here.

00:54:19.306 --> 00:54:22.976 line:80%
The first half is a smaller gathering
where the Queen Mother

00:54:23.060 --> 00:54:24.311 line:80%
and the guests mingle.

00:54:24.394 --> 00:54:25.812 line:80%
The second half is a ball.

00:54:25.896 --> 00:54:27.439 line:80%
They call it an "after-party,"

00:54:28.023 --> 00:54:31.818 line:80%
but with the guests' partners,
Cabinet members, and royal family members

00:54:31.902 --> 00:54:34.863 line:80%
all attending,
it's larger in scale than the first part.

00:54:34.946 --> 00:54:37.365 line:80%
I read an article about this
while studying abroad.

00:54:37.449 --> 00:54:38.700 line:80%
You wear gowns and dance…

00:54:38.784 --> 00:54:40.118 line:80%
That's correct.

00:54:40.202 --> 00:54:43.288 line:80%
Then what will Ms. Seong's rank be?

00:54:45.707 --> 00:54:48.001 line:80%
[Hyeon] Her rank… [chuckles]

00:54:48.085 --> 00:54:52.547 line:80%
Ms. Seong is super accomplished and all,

00:54:52.631 --> 00:54:54.216 line:80%
but she has no official rank.

00:54:55.300 --> 00:54:56.635 line:80%
-What?
-Well…

00:54:57.427 --> 00:54:59.679 line:80%
She's neither a public official

00:54:59.763 --> 00:55:01.598 line:80%
nor a noble.

00:55:01.681 --> 00:55:05.477 line:80%
[Hyejeong] So Ms. Seong will be sitting
at the very back of the room

00:55:05.560 --> 00:55:07.187 line:80%
and will always be last in line.

00:55:07.813 --> 00:55:11.942 line:80%
[chuckling]

00:55:15.862 --> 00:55:19.324 line:80%
I would be in front of the line
if I were married, right?

00:55:20.325 --> 00:55:22.494 line:80%
[chuckling]

00:55:29.876 --> 00:55:32.045 line:80%
"The attendees receive
honorary decorations

00:55:32.129 --> 00:55:35.799 line:80%
from the royal family
and gain the privilege

00:55:35.882 --> 00:55:38.969 line:80%
of accompanying the court
when it hosts diplomatic events,

00:55:39.052 --> 00:55:41.304 line:80%
starting with the year they are invited."

00:55:42.889 --> 00:55:46.935 line:80%
It is a relief that
I will never have to teach you.

00:55:47.936 --> 00:55:48.937 line:80%
[scoffs]

00:55:49.813 --> 00:55:52.232 line:80%
As if she'd ever grant me such privileges.
[smacks lips]

00:55:52.774 --> 00:55:55.610 line:80%
[phone ringing]

00:55:57.863 --> 00:55:59.364 line:80%
PRINCE

00:56:01.867 --> 00:56:02.868 line:80%
Hello?

00:56:05.370 --> 00:56:06.371 line:80%
Right now?

00:56:17.591 --> 00:56:18.842 line:80%
What's this about?

00:56:28.977 --> 00:56:29.978 line:80%
Why not?

00:56:30.478 --> 00:56:32.105 line:80%
This will be the last time.

00:56:32.189 --> 00:56:33.481 line:80%
-[chuckles]
-[♪ gentle music playing]

00:56:33.565 --> 00:56:36.943 line:80%
Where did you ever find
the nerve to wear that <i>cheollik</i>?

00:56:37.027 --> 00:56:39.154 line:80%
Was that just a stylistic choice?

00:56:39.696 --> 00:56:41.531 line:80%
I'm doing all this for your sake…

00:56:42.407 --> 00:56:43.491 line:80%
[sighs]

00:56:52.000 --> 00:56:53.001 line:80%
[sighs]

00:56:57.339 --> 00:56:58.506 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:56:59.132 --> 00:57:01.092 line:80%
Don't mind me. Just practicing.

00:57:01.885 --> 00:57:04.512 line:80%
-Practicing what?
-Walking according to rank.

00:57:05.639 --> 00:57:09.184 line:80%
I'll definitely end up walking ahead
that day if I don't practice now.

00:57:09.267 --> 00:57:11.478 line:80%
Because I'm always a trendsetter,
leading the way.

00:57:16.233 --> 00:57:17.234 line:80%
[sighs]

00:57:18.860 --> 00:57:20.111 line:80%
[sighs]

00:57:21.488 --> 00:57:23.448 line:80%
[♪ upbeat instrumental music playing]

00:57:29.079 --> 00:57:31.498 line:80%
-[chattering]
-[shutters clicking]

00:57:36.461 --> 00:57:39.547 line:80%
-A word, please!
-Please look over here!

00:57:41.341 --> 00:57:44.511 line:80%
-Over here!
-Give us a pose!

00:57:49.182 --> 00:57:52.269 line:80%
I trust all the preparations are in order?

00:57:52.894 --> 00:57:54.479 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:57:58.858 --> 00:57:59.859 line:80%
[music ends]

00:58:03.989 --> 00:58:05.240 line:80%
[sighs]

00:58:11.621 --> 00:58:12.914 line:80%
[sighs]

00:58:12.998 --> 00:58:15.000 line:80%
[♪ pensive music playing]

00:58:19.087 --> 00:58:20.380 line:80%
Bye.

00:58:22.007 --> 00:58:23.008 line:80%
[I-AN] Wait.

00:58:25.677 --> 00:58:26.678 line:80%
"Leading the way."

00:58:27.846 --> 00:58:29.014 line:80%
How do you do it?

00:58:33.810 --> 00:58:34.853 line:80%
I just never learned.

00:58:35.979 --> 00:58:38.523 line:80%
I was always the one following behind.

00:58:44.487 --> 00:58:45.989 line:80%
You just need to walk by my side.

00:58:47.949 --> 00:58:49.075 line:80%
I'll teach you.

00:59:11.431 --> 00:59:15.018 line:80%
Now that Dano, when yang energy is said
to be at its peak, has passed,

00:59:15.101 --> 00:59:17.437 line:80%
the Inner Court Banquet
has finally commenced.

00:59:17.520 --> 00:59:19.314 line:80%
<i>It's a gathering of 20 young women</i>

00:59:19.397 --> 00:59:22.317 line:80%
<i>centered around the Queen Mother,</i>
<i>the head of the Inner Court.</i>

00:59:22.400 --> 00:59:25.403 line:80%
<i>This year's guest list includes</i>
<i>Seong Huiju, CEO of Castle Beauty,</i>

00:59:25.487 --> 00:59:26.821 line:80%
<i>drawing significant attention.</i>

00:59:27.655 --> 00:59:29.741 line:80%
-[Taeju] Babe!
-You scared me.

00:59:29.824 --> 00:59:31.076 line:80%
Babe.

00:59:32.452 --> 00:59:34.037 line:80%
I found the punk who rigged her car.

00:59:35.288 --> 00:59:36.539 line:80%
You did?

00:59:36.623 --> 00:59:37.957 line:80%
Yeah, but…

00:59:38.666 --> 00:59:39.709 line:80%
But?

00:59:40.627 --> 00:59:41.795 line:80%
He's dead.

00:59:42.379 --> 00:59:44.130 line:80%
-What?
-He died.

00:59:44.756 --> 00:59:45.757 line:80%
Yesterday.

00:59:47.967 --> 00:59:49.844 line:80%
JUNIOR 4TH RANK, SENIOR 4TH RANK

00:59:49.928 --> 00:59:51.388 line:80%
JUNIOR 5TH RANK

00:59:51.471 --> 00:59:53.473 line:80%
[chattering]

00:59:56.393 --> 00:59:57.394 line:80%
JUNIOR 6TH RANK

00:59:57.477 --> 00:59:58.895 line:80%
SEONG HUIJU, COMMONER

00:59:58.978 --> 01:00:01.231 line:80%
For all her much-touted success abroad,

01:00:01.314 --> 01:00:03.024 line:80%
she was never invited.

01:00:03.108 --> 01:00:05.068 line:80%
It seems being the Grand Prince's woman

01:00:05.151 --> 01:00:07.654 line:80%
outweighs any barrier of status.

01:00:07.737 --> 01:00:10.240 line:80%
If she successfully marries him,
she will be royalty,

01:00:10.323 --> 01:00:12.283 line:80%
so they must be keeping up appearances.

01:00:12.367 --> 01:00:13.952 line:80%
Even so,

01:00:14.035 --> 01:00:16.079 line:80%
is she not someone
who caused a public scandal?

01:00:16.704 --> 01:00:18.665 line:80%
If she had been a guest last year,

01:00:18.748 --> 01:00:21.501 line:80%
at least they could have used
her achievements as an excuse.

01:00:22.460 --> 01:00:24.754 line:80%
The royal family is such a joke
these days.

01:00:24.838 --> 01:00:26.339 line:80%
[sighs]

01:00:27.757 --> 01:00:29.426 line:80%
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

01:00:30.385 --> 01:00:31.719 line:80%
SEONG HUIJU, COMMONER

01:00:32.929 --> 01:00:34.180 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:00:34.764 --> 01:00:37.058 line:80%
Were you speaking ill
of someone who is not even here?

01:00:37.142 --> 01:00:39.644 line:80%
Pardon? [chuckles]

01:00:40.228 --> 01:00:41.688 line:80%
I should have come later.

01:00:42.689 --> 01:00:43.940 line:80%
Considering you saw fit

01:00:44.691 --> 01:00:46.609 line:80%
to drag the royal family into your gossip.

01:00:47.402 --> 01:00:48.945 line:80%
[reporter] Ms. Seong, over here!

01:00:49.028 --> 01:00:51.781 line:80%
-Ms. Seong, over here!
-Please look here!

01:00:51.865 --> 01:00:54.701 line:80%
[♪ wistful music playing]

01:00:55.660 --> 01:00:57.996 line:80%
[shutters clicking]

01:01:06.713 --> 01:01:08.089 line:80%
Your Majesty.

01:01:09.132 --> 01:01:10.717 line:80%
I am Huiju of the Seong Family.

01:01:10.800 --> 01:01:12.218 line:80%
-[reporter 2] Ms. Seong.
-[reporter 3] Ms. Seong!

01:01:12.302 --> 01:01:15.221 line:80%
[reporter 2] How does it feel to be back
at the palace since going public?

01:01:15.305 --> 01:01:17.140 line:80%
[reporter 4] What was the palace's stance
on the accident?

01:01:17.223 --> 01:01:19.934 line:80%
[reporter 5] Is there a reason
why you arrived after Her Majesty?

01:01:20.018 --> 01:01:21.769 line:80%
-[reporter 6] Please give us a comment!
-[reporter 7] Please!

01:01:21.853 --> 01:01:23.813 line:80%
-We await your response.
-Give us a comment.

01:01:23.897 --> 01:01:26.483 line:80%
Unfortunately, I still do not know
my way around the palace.

01:01:27.150 --> 01:01:30.195 line:80%
I ended up losing my way for a moment.

01:01:30.278 --> 01:01:32.280 line:80%
-[shutters clicking]
-[chuckles]

01:01:35.241 --> 01:01:37.035 line:80%
Please forgive me,

01:01:37.744 --> 01:01:38.786 line:80%
Your Majesty.

01:01:47.212 --> 01:01:49.839 line:80%
I was told the Royal Secretariat
provided you with guidance.

01:01:51.007 --> 01:01:53.510 line:80%
Did you avoid wearing a <i>dangui</i>
for some particular reason?

01:01:54.469 --> 01:01:55.553 line:80%
Ah!

01:01:56.387 --> 01:01:59.891 line:80%
I was led to believe
that custom was not mandatory.

01:02:03.228 --> 01:02:04.979 line:80%
Is it not to your liking?

01:02:05.063 --> 01:02:07.065 line:80%
[shutters clicking continues]

01:02:10.401 --> 01:02:11.402 line:80%
How could it not be?

01:02:11.903 --> 01:02:13.488 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:02:21.746 --> 01:02:25.208 line:80%
-[reporter 8] Would you care to respond?
-[reporter 9] Ms. Seong, over here.

01:02:31.548 --> 01:02:32.549 line:80%
[music ends]

01:02:33.925 --> 01:02:36.427 line:80%
The snacks Your Majesty sent
for Children's Day

01:02:36.511 --> 01:02:40.515 line:80%
brought great joy to all the patients
in the pediatric ward.

01:02:40.598 --> 01:02:43.017 line:80%
I am more than happy
to help in any way I can.

01:02:43.643 --> 01:02:46.145 line:80%
Do not hesitate to let me know.

01:02:46.771 --> 01:02:49.732 line:80%
I heard Your Majesty enjoyed
my performances.

01:02:49.816 --> 01:02:53.152 line:80%
If Your Majesty could attend the next one,
I would be greatly honored…

01:03:03.788 --> 01:03:05.331 line:80%
Perhaps the summer is to thank,

01:03:05.415 --> 01:03:08.626 line:80%
but do you not find the palace grounds
even more beautiful?

01:03:08.710 --> 01:03:09.836 line:80%
Pardon?

01:03:10.503 --> 01:03:11.921 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

01:03:12.880 --> 01:03:14.173 line:80%
Let us walk a bit longer.

01:03:14.674 --> 01:03:17.677 line:80%
When the flowers are in bloom,
appreciating them is one's duty.

01:03:18.261 --> 01:03:19.971 line:80%
-Yes, Your Majesty.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

01:03:22.849 --> 01:03:24.851 line:80%
[guests gasping, exclaiming]

01:03:41.326 --> 01:03:44.329 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

01:03:58.259 --> 01:03:59.260 line:80%
[chuckles]

01:04:11.981 --> 01:04:13.441 line:80%
Please teach me.

01:04:15.526 --> 01:04:16.778 line:80%
Now that I am by your side.

01:04:18.613 --> 01:04:20.615 line:80%
[music continues]

01:04:56.818 --> 01:04:57.985 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>Do not bend to their will.</i>

01:04:59.737 --> 01:05:00.738 line:80%
<i>Do not step back</i>

01:05:01.656 --> 01:05:02.907 line:80%
<i>and do not compromise.</i>

01:05:04.992 --> 01:05:06.536 line:80%
<i>I shall fight with all that I have.</i>

01:05:11.666 --> 01:05:12.667 line:80%
<i>Just as you do.</i>

01:05:27.724 --> 01:05:30.643 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN

01:05:30.727 --> 01:05:33.521 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

01:06:06.721 --> 01:06:09.724 line:80%
[interviewer] <i>From when you were</i>
<i>just acquaintances to now,</i>

01:06:09.807 --> 01:06:11.517 line:80%
<i>what would you say is the biggest change?</i>

01:06:11.601 --> 01:06:13.144 line:80%
Being overprotective?

01:06:13.227 --> 01:06:14.145 line:80%
[I-AN] <i>That's a bit too naive, no?</i>

01:06:14.228 --> 01:06:18.274 line:80%
A businesswoman should know better
than to trust people so easily.

01:06:18.858 --> 01:06:20.359 line:80%
<i>There's a spy at my private residence.</i>

01:06:21.027 --> 01:06:22.195 line:80%
Seong Huiju!

01:06:22.278 --> 01:06:24.989 line:80%
Don't you find him to be so impatient?

01:06:27.158 --> 01:06:28.451 line:20%
Your Royal Highness?

01:06:28.534 --> 01:06:30.536 line:20%
Will you give me your hand in marriage?

01:06:30.620 --> 01:06:32.663 line:20%
[Yun] <i>Did you think</i>
<i>I would simply let this stand?</i>

01:06:32.747 --> 01:06:33.873 line:20%
Announce me.

01:06:33.956 --> 01:06:36.793 line:20%
[Jeongwoo] <i>How could I refuse a request</i>
<i>from the Queen Mother?</i>

01:06:38.002 --> 01:06:39.879 line:20%
[I-AN] <i>You should only have eyes for me.</i>

01:06:40.379 --> 01:06:42.715 line:20%
<i>As if we were hopelessly in love.</i>

01:06:49.847 --> 01:06:56.854 line:20%
EPILOGUE

01:07:00.525 --> 01:07:02.527 line:20%
Oh! [gasps]

01:07:04.821 --> 01:07:05.822 line:20%
[grunts]

01:07:05.905 --> 01:07:07.907 line:20%
[♪ comical music playing]

01:07:10.618 --> 01:07:13.788 line:20%
[whistling, clears throat]

01:07:17.667 --> 01:07:18.668 line:20%
Wait.

01:07:20.378 --> 01:07:21.379 line:20%
You…

01:07:23.756 --> 01:07:25.091 line:20%
[clears throat]

01:07:25.174 --> 01:07:26.259 line:20%
You did well

01:07:27.218 --> 01:07:28.553 line:20%
during the exhibition match.

01:07:31.681 --> 01:07:34.684 line:20%
Are you trying to take credit?

01:07:37.770 --> 01:07:38.813 line:20%
"Take credit"?

01:07:38.896 --> 01:07:41.023 line:20%
Do you not grasp
the concept of a compliment?

01:07:43.401 --> 01:07:44.443 line:20%
I guess not.

01:07:48.197 --> 01:07:49.198 line:20%
[sighs]

01:08:08.551 --> 01:08:09.594 line:20%
[clears throat]

01:08:12.138 --> 01:08:13.389 line:20%
[sighs]

01:08:17.727 --> 01:08:19.270 line:20%
Darn it, you scared me.

01:08:20.354 --> 01:08:21.772 line:20%
Have you been there?

01:08:22.315 --> 01:08:23.441 line:20%
-Yes.
-Since when?

01:08:24.692 --> 01:08:26.444 line:20%
Before you started lingering.

01:08:26.527 --> 01:08:28.112 line:20%
[♪ pop music playing]

01:08:29.906 --> 01:08:30.907 line:20%
[clears throat]

01:08:39.999 --> 01:08:42.043 line:20%
Are you close to Seong Huiju?

01:08:44.754 --> 01:08:46.797 line:20%
We're close.
We live in the same dorms too.

01:08:48.090 --> 01:08:49.300 line:20%
What is she like?

01:08:56.933 --> 01:08:58.142 line:20%
She's pretty.

01:09:00.144 --> 01:09:01.437 line:20%
Yeah, she is.

01:09:13.699 --> 01:09:15.701 line:80%
Translated by Justin S. Kim

01:09:15.785 --> 01:09:17.745 line:80%
[♪ pop music playing]

01:09:27.046 --> 01:09:30.716 line:80%
PERFECT CROWN